summary: Allows passage between levels in Tel Mithryn without the glitchy lift
descriptionHtml:
I got tired of having to turn collision off and on to get to the upper level of Tel Mithryn and back. This doesn\'t fix the lift. What it does is adds 2 trap doors in the area to allow you to get up and down without having to deal with the non-functioning lift.

(Works until they actually fix it.)

Enjoy :)

==
If you like this, don\'t forget to look up my other mods. Do a search for \"Higher Magic\" to get the list. :)
author: Pan Dragondagger --- aka -  Rex1029
